    'body' => 'Joe Pettit <jpettit@ix.netcom.com> wrote:

>TravelrTNE wrote:
>> There are "zoom wombs" that can do the cloning pretty fast.  It\'s a 
>> few weeks to grow a full human body to maturity.  I suspect a sirloin 
