    'date' => 'Tue, 26 May 1998 09:49:10  0400 (EDT)',
    'body' => 'Howdy!

Steve Rennell wrote:
> "David P. Summers" <summers@alum.mit.edu> wrote:
> > I personally would punt transponders.
> > I really don\'t see much interest in them.  If the Imperium
